   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Sourcing Events</uicontrol> tab.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the appropriate sourcing event and click <uicontrol>View</uicontrol>. </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206028/69206106.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>RFI</uicontrol> tab.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>View RFI.</uicontrol>
            </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206028/69206097.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To download the RFI, click <uicontrol>Download</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>A file with an extension .xls will start downloading. To view the downloaded file, click on <uicontrol>RFI.xls</uicontrol> .</p>
               </note>
               <p>
                  <fig>
                     <image placement="break"
                            width="700"
                            href="../attachments/69206028/69206108.png"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To respond to RFI, click <uicontrol>Create Response</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206028/69206112.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the appropriate responses.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To upload an attachment, click <uicontrol>Upload.</uicontrol>
            </p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig>
                     <image placement="break"
                            width="700"
                            href="../attachments/69206028/69206043.png"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>For the <uicontrol>Attachments</uicontrol> in Apttus STP, you can upload any file. We allow files of the following extension types: (.PDF), (.RTF), (.RTX), (.TXT), (.JPG), (.JPEG), (.PNG), (.GIF), (.TIF), (.BMP), (.DOC), (.DOCX), (.DOCM), (.PPT), (.PPTX), (.PPTM), (.PPS), (.PPSX), (.XLS), (.XLSX), (.XLSM), (.ZIP), (.MP3), (.M4A), (.OGG), (.WAV), (.MP4), (.M4V), (.MOV), (.OGV), (.3GP), (.3G2). The application might become slow if you upload a file higher than 25 MB.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Choose File</uicontrol> and select the appropriate file.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the <uicontrol>File</uicontrol>
               <uicontrol>Description</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the appropriate permission from the Permissions picklist menu.</p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <table>
                     <tgroup cols="2">
                        <thead>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Permission</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Description</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Public</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>To make the attachment available to all the Suppliers.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Private</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>To make the attachment available to only the Buyer.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                           <row>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>Selective Public</p>
                              </entry>
                              <entry>
                                 <p>To make the attachment available to the selected Supplier(s).</p>
                                 <p>Note: At least one supplier must be selected for this option.</p>
                              </entry>
                           </row>
                        </tbody>
                     </tgroup>
                  </table>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Attach.</uicontrol>
            </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="550"
                         href="../attachments/14680532/15630649.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To edit an attachment, click <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To delete an attachment, click <uicontrol>Delete</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206028/69206110.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To submit your responses to the buyer, click <uicontrol>Submit Response</uicontrol>. </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="700"
                         href="../attachments/69206028/69206107.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Back to Sourcing Event </uicontrol>
               <uicontrol>link</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>Once you submit your response to the buyer, <uicontrol>View RFI</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>View Response</uicontrol> links are visible on the Sourcing Event Detail page. You can edit the responses before the RFI deadline. To edit the responses, Click <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol>. To download the responses, click <uicontrol>Download</uicontrol>. Ensure that you click <uicontrol>Submit Response</uicontrol> after you have edited the response.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
</topic>
